long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
SEO Extension - Get SEO insights instantly! Built by full-time SEOs, Get in-depth Meta Data analysis at the click of a button.

Key Features:
* Find All Basic Meta Data like SEO Heading, Description.
* Images - Find Anchor, Title Details to fix any incomplete data.
* Links - Get Insight about Internal and External links, which helps in fixing any linking issue in website.
* Schema - Find Schema details and improve your website.
